@startuml approach1-linq-abbreviated
title **Approach 1: InMemoryContainer — LINQ Query Flow (Abbreviated)**

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2

actor "Test Code" as Test
participant "InMemoryFeedIteratorSetup" as Setup
participant "InMemoryContainer" as IMC
participant "IOrderedQueryable<T>" as Queryable
participant "CosmosOverridable\nFeedIteratorExtensions" as Ext
participant "InMemoryFeedIterator<T>" as FeedIter

note over Setup
  Called once per test fixture:
  InMemoryFeedIteratorSetup.Register()
end note

Test -> IMC ++ : GetItemLinqQueryable<T>()
IMC -> IMC : GetAllItemsForPartition()\n→ Deserialize → .AsQueryable()
IMC -> Queryable ** : IOrderedQueryable<T>\n(LINQ-to-Objects)
IMC --> Test -- : IOrderedQueryable<T>

Test -> Queryable : .Where() / .Select() / .OrderBy()\n(LINQ-to-Objects operators)

Test -> Ext ++ : .ToFeedIteratorOverridable()
Ext -> Setup : CreateInMemoryFeedIterator<T>()
Setup -> FeedIter ** : InMemoryFeedIterator<T>
Ext --> Test -- : FeedIterator<T>

loop while HasMoreResults
  Test -> FeedIter ++ : ReadNextAsync()
  FeedIter --> Test -- : FeedResponse<T>
end

@enduml
